<li class='cover' id='bookCover_93007'>
<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/93007.The_Merry_Adventures_of_Robin_Hood"><img alt="The Merry Adventures of Robin Hood" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1389006722l/93007._SX98_.jpg" />
